gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 118, Trail Blazers 114
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Blazers, 118-114. Klay Thompson led Golden State with 28 points as Andrew Wiggins added 25 points and seven rebounds. Jerami Grant totaled 30 points, seven rebounds, and six assists for Portland as Anfernee Simons chipped in 24 points and seven assists. The Warriors improve to 12-14 as the Blazers move to 6-19.
